profile:
We specialize in professional cabinet refinishing using eco-friendly, water-based lacquers to achieve a quality, factory finish.  In business for over 16 years, we excel in punctuality, communication, and attention to detail.  We offer a three year warranty, as well as free in-home consultations.  Email us today to either get an estimate right online or book an appointment!  We look forward to working with you.

Kindest Regards,

Rachel Germain: Co-Director/Owner

Zack Hounsome: Co-Director/Owner

The EcoRefinishers Team
